Things look a little different around here! That s because CBS All Access is now Paramount . It s everything you love about CBS All Access but with even MORE to explore like: LIVE SPORTS: Catch edge of your seat action with CBS Sports like the NFL UEFA more along with highlights replays expert analysis from the best in the game on CBS Sports HQ. BREAKING NEWS: Never miss out on breaking CBS news award winning reporting in depth interviews. And with CBSN national CBSN local you ll be in the loop 24 7. A MOUNTAIN OF ENTERTAINMENT: Watch the best in live events reality competitions hit movies and tens of thousands of episodes from CBS BET Comedy Central MTV Nickelodeon and Smithsonian Channel along with Paramount Originals exclusive shows and movies you ll only catch here.

Improved support for Apple s TV app. Fixed a Live TV crash that can happen after denying location. Fixed a Live TV issue where under certain circumstances Live TV plays in the background or results in a blank screen.

Fixed an issue with Live TV that prevented the player and schedule from appearing. Fixed an issue where Live TV would not play on app launch following device sleep. Fixed an bug that prevented photos from loading. Corrected some issues related to video player scrubbing. Fixed some issues related to closed captions.
Fixed a crash in Live TV Fixed a UI issue when the app is launched from a deeplink Fixed an issue where under certain conditions a user was unable to restore purchase

Fixed a crash bug that could occur when viewing Big Brother: Over the Top live feeds. Various improvements and bug fixes.
Fixed a crash issue related to the video player. We heard you pun intended ! You will now hear audio even if your device switch is set to silent.

We fixed some bugs that slipped through in the last release. We had updated the video player to fix some bugs and new bugs popped up. Thank you for your feedback and helping us to catch these issues. Sorry for the headaches that we caused and please accept this release as our apology. Specifically we: Fixed crashes that occur during video playback Fixed issue when trying to cast video to Chromecast Fixed issue when loading and switching between Big Brother live feeds Made updates to security
